<section class="w-full bg-black grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 border-b-[6px] border-[#d39a4d] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative z-20 flex items-center bg-black py-16 px-8 sm:py-20 sm:px-16 lg:py-28 lg:pl-24 lg:pr-16">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[42px] text-white font-bold leading-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-xl" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        CENTRAL FLORIDA'S TRUSTED<br/>MOBILE DETAILING EXPERTS
      </h2>
      <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[#d39a4d] mb-8 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(211,154,77,0.5)]"></div>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-loose mb-6" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
        At Central FLA. Auto Detail LLC, we bring the detail shop to you — anywhere in Central Florida. Backed by years of hands-on experience, our team takes pride in treating every vehicle like it's our own, delivering results that speak for themselves.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-loose mb-10" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
