      </p>
      <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-[#d39a4d] to-[#fdd78c] text-black font-bold text-xs tracking-widest py-4 px-8 rounded-sm hover:bg-[#fdd78c] hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
        BOOK YOUR APPOINTMENT
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full h-[320px] sm:h-[450px] lg:h-auto min-h-full relative overflow-hidden -mt-[2px] lg:mt-0 lg:-ml-[2px] z-10">
